graph LR
    ODHModelController[odh-model-controller]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ODHModelController -->|required<br/>CRDs| KServe[KServe v0.12.1]
    ODHModelController -->|required<br/>external access| OpenShiftRoutes[OpenShift Routes 3.9.0+]
    ODHModelController -->|required<br/>webhook TLS| CertManager[cert-manager or<br/>OCP Service CA]

    %% External Dependencies (Conditional)
    ODHModelController -->|conditional<br/>serverless mode| Knative[Knative Serving v0.39.3]
    ODHModelController -->|conditional<br/>mTLS, routing| Istio[Istio/Service Mesh v1.19.4]
    ODHModelController -->|conditional<br/>auth/authz| Authorino[Authorino v0.15.0]
    ODHModelController -->|conditional<br/>monitoring| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.64.1]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODHModelController -->|reads config<br/>CRD watch| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator<br/>DataScienceCluster<br/>DSCInitialization]
    ODHModelController -->|optional<br/>model metadata| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>gRPC API]
    ODHModelController -->|enrolls namespaces<br/>ServiceMeshMember| ServiceMeshCP[Service Mesh<br/>Control Plane]

    %% Integration Points (Components that use odh-model-controller)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management<br/>InferenceService CRUD| ODHModelController
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|auto-deploy models<br/>creates InferenceService| ODHModelController
    KServeController[KServe Controller] -.->|collaboration<br/>watches same CRDs| ODHModelController

    %% External Services (Runtime)
    ODHModelController -.->|inference pods access<br/>HTTPS/443| S3[S3 Storage<br/>Model Artifacts]
    ODHModelController -->|resource mgmt<br/>HTTPS/6443| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]

    %% CRD Dependencies (What CRDs odh-model-controller watches)
    subgraph "Watched CRDs"
        InferenceServiceCRD[InferenceService<br/>serving.kserve.io]
        ServingRuntimeCRD[ServingRuntime<br/>serving.kserve.io]
        PredictorCRD[Predictor<br/>serving.kserve.io<br/>ModelMesh]
    end

    InferenceServiceCRD -.->|watched by| ODHModelController
    ServingRuntimeCRD -.->|watched by| ODHModelController
    PredictorCRD -.->|watched by| ODHModelController

    %% Created Resources (What odh-model-controller creates)
    subgraph "Creates Resources"
        Route[Routes<br/>OpenShift]
        Gateway[Gateways<br/>Istio]
        VirtualService[VirtualServices<br/>Istio]
        PeerAuth[PeerAuthentications<br/>Istio]
        AuthConfig[AuthConfigs<br/>Authorino]
        ServiceMonitor[ServiceMonitors<br/>Prometheus]
        NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicies<br/>K8s]
    end

    ODHModelController -.->|creates| Route
    ODHModelController -.->|creates| Gateway
    ODHModelController -.->|creates| VirtualService
    ODHModelController -.->|creates| PeerAuth
    ODHModelController -.->|creates| AuthConfig
    ODHModelController -.->|creates| ServiceMonitor
    ODHModelController -.->|creates| NetworkPolicy

    %% Styling
    style ODHModelController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies (required)
    style KServe fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style OpenShiftRoutes fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style CertManager fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies (conditional)
    style Knative fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Authorino fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style PrometheusOp fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% Internal ODH dependencies
    style ODHOperator fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style ServiceMeshCP fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
